{"tid":512774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那反聖誕蔓延香港！黑衣男縱火燒香港機場聖誕樹！","createTime":"2017-12-29T00:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T01:46:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8f64ac7160c1a55f4a8a6e8de5106fcf4902ef","tid":512774,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:03:30.000Z","msg":"機場1號客運大樓門外花槽，佈置四棵約3呎高聖誕樹。凌晨約2時28分，其中一棵聖誕樹突告起火焚燒，職員發現報警。消防員到場開喉將火救熄。火警中無人受傷及毋須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n職員翻查現場閉路電視錄影，發現一名身穿黑衫黑褲男子，行近花槽聖誕樹，離開不久即發生火警。警方調查有可疑，將案列縱火處理，追緝涉案男子下落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514491067_f163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514491067_f163.jpg&h=3ca4f7ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514491081_94a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514491081_94a6.jpg&h=0466bd8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514491099_294d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514491099_294d.jpg&h=3a7373e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171229/large/1514491110_e75e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171229%2Flarge%2F1514491110_e75e.jpg&h=a3d95019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"840ec743804f9aee0d43a61925f760f833d367de","tid":512774,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:53:26.000Z","msg":"又係啲廢老做"},{"pid":"734480b93e4a78fff7589acf8f2198faf27511c4","tid":512774,"uid":116289,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"支那=人類毒瘤"},{"